Text: Hey  "sistromo", if you have better books, please make a torrent and upload them. I clicked on your name and noticed you're not sharing anything, just taking. It's a two way street dude. You have to give to receive.

Bansky, Casteneda, Steiner - there's no way "sistromo" even read the file list. Yes, some flaky, newage - rhymes with sewage ;-) stuff, but a nice mix of well, precisely what the torrent title says.  Thanks for sharing this, and for the individual files. Take only what you need.
What the hell, I'll d/l the whole thing. Maybe there is some truth to that "hollow earth" theory...

It appears you have downloaded my 'Road to Enlightenment' collection - as you seem to have most (or all) of my collection in here. Glad to see it is being shared some more.. and nice additions, I will be download -- Gracias!
